					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Other ideas I've been musing with is What could you achieve with reworked motherboards, take components of the day but rework them. Say you have a PPU and then add another chip that does sprites, a TMS something <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /> then put another 6502 are higher clock, so you have a GPU cpu and an game CPU, more of an arcade machine design. The C128 offers a lot of potential in this area.</div>

